window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He left to see the world, but the world is a cruel master</b></p> <p>Setting out to be a wandering cultivator, Sen has high ideals. Half-remembered stories of honorable cultivators and the kindness of his teachers shaped his expectations.</p> <p>The world he finds is something else entirely. Thrust into deadly conflict, Sen finds himself fleeing the death of a sect cultivator in fear of retribution. As his flight carries him across the kingdom, he finds his ideals challenged by bandits, cultivators, and demon beasts.</p> <p>In the city of Emperors Bay he will face the true crucible of his character and skills, and discover the harsh truth that violence is necessary to survive.</p>"; 
